      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-hero ci-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"ci-hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"ci-kicker\">AAW</p>\n      <h1>What are Custom<em>In-Ear Monitors?</em></h1>\n      <p class=\"ci-dek\">A custom in-ear monitor is not a louder earbud. It is an acoustic instrument built around the unique shape of your ear, tuned to a reference curve, and finished by hand. This article explains the concept, the science, and why custom matters.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ci-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-hero-ciem-2026.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW custom in-ear monitors \u2014 the intersection of precision acoustics and personal fit\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" loading=\"eager\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"ci-stat-strip\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap ci-stats\">\n      <div class=\"ci-stat\"><b>Personalised Anatomy</b><span>Each shell is 3D-modelled from your individual ear impressions. No two pairs are alike, and the fit is exclusive to you.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ci-stat\"><b>Superior Isolation</b><span>A full-shell custom monitor blocks up to 26 dB of ambient noise passively, without batteries or active circuitry.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ci-stat\"><b>Multi-Driver Architecture</b><span>AAW CIEMs use balanced armature, dynamic, and hybrid configurations with precision crossover networks for coherent sound.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ci-stat\"><b>Hand-Built in Singapore</b><span>Every AAW custom monitor is assembled and finished at 76 Playfair Rd by the same technicians who tune our flagship universals.</span></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "content_width": "large",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "primary",
        "top_space_desktop": 0,
