    "ci_usecases": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ci-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ci-kicker\">Use Cases</p>\n        <h2>Who Relies on Custom Monitors</h2>\n        <p>Custom in-ear monitors are not exclusive to one type of listener. They serve distinct roles across the music industry and beyond, each application benefiting from a different combination of isolation, accuracy, and comfort.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-usecase-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ci-usecase-card\">\n          <h3>Stage Musicians</h3>\n          <p>The original and most demanding use case. A performing musician needs to hear their own instrument, the click track, and the monitor mix over a live PA system that can exceed 110 dB. A CIEM provides the isolation and clarity to monitor at a safe volume without removing the performer from the audience energy. Vocalists, guitarists, drummers, and keyboardists all benefit from custom fit and stage-ready durability.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-usecase-card\">\n          <h3>Audiophiles &amp; Enthusiasts</h3>\n          <p>For the critical listener, a CIEM removes the variables. There is no tip-rolling, no seal inconsistency, and no question about whether you are hearing the IEM or the fit. The driver sits at a known distance from the eardrum, and the shell acts as a controlled acoustic chamber. This makes a CIEM the most direct path from the recording to your perception of it.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-usecase-card\">\n          <h3>Audio Engineers &amp; Producers</h3>\n          <p>A portable reference monitor that sounds the same in a hotel room, a flight, and a studio control room is invaluable. Engineers use CIEMs to check mixes, evaluate masters, and make EQ decisions they can trust. The consistency of a custom shell means the stereo image and tonal balance do not shift between listening sessions.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-usecase-card\">\n          <h3>Everyday Listeners</h3>\n          <p>Not every CIEM owner performs on stage. Many choose custom for the daily experience: commuting with total isolation, working in open-plan offices without distraction, or simply enjoying music at its most detailed. A CIEM is a long-term investment in how you hear \u2014 and it fits no one else, which makes it deeply personal.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
