    "ci_why_aaw": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-section\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ci-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ci-kicker\">Why AAW</p>\n        <h2>Singapore Craft, Global Standard</h2>\n        <p>AAW has been designing and building in-ear monitors since 2014 from a single workshop at 76 Playfair Road in Singapore. Every custom monitor is 3D-printed, hand-finished, assembled, and measured under one roof. Here is what sets our approach apart.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-approach-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ci-approach-card\">\n          <h3>In-House Manufacturing</h3>\n          <p>Unlike brands that outsource shell production or driver assembly, AAW controls the entire build pipeline. Ear impressions are 3D-scanned on-site. Shells are printed in our own lab. Drivers are installed and crossed over by hand. Every pair is measured on an audio analyser and listened to before it ships. When something goes wrong, the person who built your monitor is in the same building as the person who will fix it.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Driver Expertise</h3>\n          <p>AAW has shipped hybrid, tribrid, and all-BA configurations across multiple product generations. Our flagship Canary Pro uses a 12-driver hybrid architecture with a dynamic low-end, balanced armature mids and highs, and a four-way passive crossover. From the entry-level A3H+ Lux to the reference Z07, each platform is tuned to a coherent target rather than chasing driver count alone.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Tuning Philosophy</h3>\n          <p>We tune for musicality, not for a graph. Every AAW monitor is voiced by ear before it is validated by measurement. The goal is a sound that is engaging and fatigue-free over hours of listening \u2014 whether that is a warm, lush signature for long sessions or a flat, analytical curve for critical work. Our custom monitors follow the same tuning targets as our universal line, so what you audition in a demo unit is what you receive in your custom build.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-note\" style=\"margin-top:32px;\">\n        <strong>Visit our workshop</strong>\n        <p>Our showroom at 76 Playfair Rd, #01-03 LHK2 Building is open for auditions and ear impression services. Hear the full AAW lineup, compare custom and universal models side by side, and get your impressions taken by our trained staff. <a href=\"/pages/contact\">Book an appointment</a> or walk in during business hours.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
