    "ci_process": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ci-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ci-kicker\">The Process</p>\n        <h2>From Impression to First Listen</h2>\n        <p>Building a CIEM takes approximately two to four weeks from the day we receive your ear impressions. Here is what happens at each stage of the build.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-process-steps\">\n        <div class=\"ci-process-step\">\n          <div class=\"ci-step-num\">1</div>\n          <h4>Impression Scan</h4>\n          <p>Your physical impressions arrive at our lab and are 3D-scanned into our modelling software within one business day. We confirm receipt by email.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-process-step\">\n          <div class=\"ci-step-num\">2</div>\n          <h4>Shell Design</h4>\n          <p>A technician models the shell geometry around the driver layout, ensuring sufficient internal volume and nozzle alignment. Faceplate artwork is prepared.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-process-step\">\n          <div class=\"ci-step-num\">3</div>\n          <h4>3D Printing</h4>\n          <p>The shell body and faceplate are printed in medical-grade acrylic. Support material is removed and the surfaces are hand-finished to a smooth, bio-compatible polish.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-process-step\">\n          <div class=\"ci-step-num\">4</div>\n          <h4>Driver Assembly</h4>\n          <p>Drivers are installed, the crossover is soldered, and acoustic tubing is routed to the nozzle. Each connection is checked under magnification before the shell is sealed.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-process-step\">\n          <div class=\"ci-step-num\">5</div>\n          <h4>QC &amp; Listening</h4>\n          <p>Every pair is measured on our audio analyser for channel matching and frequency response. A final listening check confirms the monitor meets our tuning target before it is packed and shipped.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-subhead\">Universal vs Custom at a glance</div>\n      <div class=\"ci-compare-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell header\"><h4>Feature</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell header\"><h4>Universal IEM</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell header\"><h4>Custom IEM</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell label\"><span>Fit</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>Standardised shape with interchangeable tips; fit varies by tip choice and ear anatomy</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Moulded from your ear impressions; identical fit every session</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell label\"><span>Isolation</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>Varies by tip material and seal quality; typically \u221215 to \u221220 dB</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Consistent full-shell seal; up to \u221226 dB passive isolation</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell label\"><span>Sound Consistency</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>Insertion depth varies with each wear, shifting bass response and stereo image</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Fixed driver-to-eardrum distance; repeatable frequency response</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell label\"><span>Comfort (3h+)</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>Tips can cause pressure points and fatigue over long periods</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Weight distributed across concha; designed for hours of wear</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell label\"><span>Personalisation</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>Limited to cable and tip choices; shell is standard</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Full control over shell colour, faceplate material, artwork, and engraving</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell label\"><span>Lead Time</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>In stock; ships within days</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ci-compare-cell\"><p>2\u20134 weeks from receipt of impressions</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
